ss=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b5e5c42defe925138147136d91d1a063f36c7df","tid":2261580,"uid":94480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T02:27:09.000Z","msg":"最後淪為黑社會行刑器具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1ea4a9332fee81bd7c3450e3b5c818589afabc9","tid":2261580,"uid":169708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"336958e909cf530ca9f8bb88f7bbf06f733e5910","tid":2261580,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T12:11:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2785000/2786813/bian0_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2785000%2F2786813%2Fbian0_1024.jpg&h=48244c2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不少人都討厭踎廁，畢竟姿勢並不舒服，去得太久雙腳會很累。為了解決這個問題，淘寳近年湧現「蹲改坐便神器」之類的商品，引起不少網民熱議！<br />\n<br />\n淘寶網購平台出現了不少聲稱可以折疊的「蹲改坐便神器」，只要安裝好就能直接將踎廁變座廁。如果將「神器」折疊起來，也能正常地使用踎廁。這樣，方便長者、孕婦、腿傷人士使用的同時，又不影響喜歡踎廁的用家。店家表示，這個設計適用家庭、醫院、養老院，甚至是商場、酒店，用途十分多。<br />\n<br />\n然而，不少網民似乎就有其他擔憂。有網民指出「踎廁神器」的設計「中空」，加上固定的方法似乎很兒戲，不少網民都笑說：「啪一聲斷咗即時變屎撈人」、「你肯定個嘢真係穩陣？」、「要學習壓水花」、「肚痾嗰陣成腳 ...」、「一肚痾。真係一腳都係」、「深水炸彈」、「大便跳水台」。對此，店家就表示「蹲改坐便神器」能承重 600 斤（約 300 公斤），而且有些設計就在腿前附帶擋板，不知大家又怎樣看？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2785000/2786813/bian3_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2785000%2F2786813%2Fbian3_600.jpg&h=cd18737f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n淘寳「蹲改坐便神器」引起不少網民熱議。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2785000/2786813/bian5_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2785000%2F2786813%2Fbian5_600.jpg&h=2225d69f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n只要安裝好就能直接將踎廁變座廁，不用只要折疊即可。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T02:29:56.000Z","msg":"爆石爆到周圍都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d15dee3af07870be554de6e72b582e3811167aa","tid":2261580,"uid":364767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T02:31:30.000Z","msg":"咁嘅設計 邊度夠成托力㗎！"},{"pid":"ec978d63aefcbdf67860a16635735fe09390fc4e","tid":2261580,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d15dee3af07870be554de6e72b582e3811167aa","tid":2261580,"uid":364767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T02:31:30.000Z","msg":"咁嘅設計 邊度夠成托力㗎！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T02:39:30.000Z","msg":"個骹唔爛，塊板都唔用得耐"},{"pid":"9e6e1f02fde79a68c3a0db9a7f9224d661f2b3f4","tid":2261580,"uid":10023,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T02:45:58.000Z","msg":"我想知踎廁點樣同時痾屎+尿<br />\n有無教學"},{"pid":"1dd4e4665a699cb9bc85df0004920ecbd8f6b66a","tid":2261580,"uid":195136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbfb9ff91cce580e24a83b0fa01acd93aa1f8295","tid":2261580,"uid":59976,"like":7,"dislike":21,"score":-14,"quote":{"pid":"abff645eae5c02e4c73c4dcb25612cfc542458e0","tid":2261580,"uid":335434,"like":94,"dislike":3,"score":91,"quote":{"pid":"81f3076fbb9909b9c09139456ce75988241d5dba","tid":2261580,"uid":109629,"like":160,"dislike":18,"score":142,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T12:19:03.000Z","msg":"踎廁呢啲反人類文明既野根撚本就要淘汰<br />\n好好地安個馬桶算把啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T12:21:09.000Z","msg":"對啲未有文明嘅地方嚟講痞踎廁先係prefect match嚟呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T12:23:26.000Z","msg":"日本仲有好多踎廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"cite